s, they are good enough for us. Feel your shoe-drobe is missing a key pair? Now is the time to swing by charity shops or hunt on secondhand sites for ones with original scuffing included.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTopsy-turvy layering\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"eac80659-4746-4e41-86c2-8173de8b9b17\" data-spacefinder-role=\"inline\" data-spacefinder-type=\"model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.ImageBlockElement\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"img-5\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/62828aca93349468b90724ae0363a7931cb6c639/0_0_3890_4862/master/3890.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 660px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/62828aca93349468b90724ae0363a7931cb6c639/0_0_3890_4862/master/3890.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/62828aca93349468b90724ae0363a7931cb6c639/0_0_3890_4862/master/3890.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/62828aca93349468b90724ae0363a7931cb6c639/0_0_3890_4862/master/3890.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/62828aca93349468b90724ae0363a7931cb6c639/0_0_3890_4862/master/3890.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 320px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 320px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/62828aca93349468b90724ae0363a7931cb6c639/0_0_3890_4862/maste